title: Amenities You Deserve at 1500 Nicollet! Lease This 2 Bedroom Today!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'HURRY – our new rent-restricted apartments are going fast!', 'Submit your application paperwork quickly and easily today to reserve your brand-new home!', 'The search for your perfect home stops here!', '1500', 'Nicollet is one of Minneapolis’ best recently constructed apartment communities that has all the amenities that you could ever want.', 'Our spacious apartments have a full-size washer & dryer in EVERY home, modern interior designs, individually controlled heating & air-conditioning, large windows providing tons of natural light, and energy efficient lighting & appliances.', '1500 Nicollet features a cozy community room with a fireplace & kitchen, a coffee & tech bar, a huge outdoor courtyard area with grilling & picnic areas, an on-site fitness center & yoga studio, and much more.', 'Reserve your one, two or three bedroom home today!', 'Specific layouts & square footage may vary according to specific floor plan types.', 'All finishes & appliances are the same in every home.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Professional, On-Site Management Team', '- WaterSense Plumbing Fixtures', '- Heated Underground Parking Available (Additional fee of $145/month - based on availability)', '- Easy Access To Public Transportation', '- On-Site Fitness Center & Yoga Studio', '- Community Kitchen', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', 'See Respective Floor Plan Info -', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 11:00AM-6:00PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', '1500 Nicollet', '1500 Nicollet Ave.', 'South', 'Minneapolis, MN, 55403', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '0lz0MvU1']
